data.description: Don't miss out on these water views and the desirable upgrades throughout in this hard-to-find and spacious Morningside Lane model located in the gated Stone Creek Golf Course Community.  Tons of curb appeal with stacked stone accents, a covered front porch for relaxing, mature landscaping, and decorative concrete curbing, this beautiful home is built to impress. A custom-built, glass inlay Andersen storm door with sidelight opens to the versatile and open floor plan featuring 3 Bedrooms and 3 ½ bathrooms in a light and bright, neutral color palette with crown molding, recessed lighting, Key West style shutters, Casablanca fans throughout, and diagonally laid 20x20 porcelain tile floors.  Stunningly appointed Chef's kitchen with upgraded stainless appliances and vent hood, granite countertops, soft close drawers, a large walk-in pantry, above and below cabinet lighting, a solar tube skylight, and elegant pendant lighting. The Kitchen is open to a casual dining area and a Great Room with two sets of expansive sliders open to a large paver-lined Florida room and patio perfect for outdoor entertaining overlooking priceless water views. The Owner's Suite offers a spacious custom-designed walk-in closet and en suite bath featuring a large double sink vanity with granite countertops and soft close drawers, a massive Roman-style shower, and a separate water closet. LED lighting throughout, tinted windows and an attic solar exhaust fan for added energy efficiency, a Nuvo H2O Manor Plus Eco-friendly water softener and filtration system, a bonus office/den, and a convenient half bath are just a few more fantastic features in this home that you will not want to miss. Move in and enjoy fantastic community activities and amenities including a golf course, resort-style pools, a health spa, trips and entertainment, and more!
